                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18311201-211-off1125 t18311201-211-crimeloc1128"></join>. On the 26th of November the prisoner had a glass of beer and the newspaper in the parlour; he came out and went into the street - I went into the parlour, saw the candle taken out of the candlestick, and put into a glass, lighted; I followed, and saw him in Marylebone-street - he ran away; I called stop thief! he threw one candlestick down, which was given to me, and he was secured.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
